34#ifndef _RSALIST_H
35#define _RSALIST_H
36
37#include <netinet/in.h>
38#include <openssl/rsa.h>
39
40#include "handler.h"
41#include "genlist.h"
42
43enum rsa_key_type {
44 RSA_TYPE_ANY = 0,
45 RSA_TYPE_PUBLIC,
46 RSA_TYPE_PRIVATE
47};
48
49struct rsa_key {
50 struct netaddr *src;
51 struct netaddr *dst;
52 RSA *rsa;
53};
54
55int rsa_key_insert(struct genlist *list, struct netaddr *src, struct netaddr *dst, RSA *rsa);
56struct rsa_key *rsa_key_dup(struct rsa_key *key);
57void rsa_key_free(void *data);
58void rsa_key_dump(struct genlist *list);
59
60struct genlist *rsa_lookup_keys(struct ph1handle *iph1, int my);
61RSA *rsa_try_check_rsasign(vchar_t *source, vchar_t *sig, struct genlist *list);
62
63unsigned long rsa_list_count(struct genlist *list);
64
65int rsa_parse_file(struct genlist *list, const char *fname, enum rsa_key_type type);
66
67#endif /* _RSALIST_H */
